  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink253-kilavi">varaiviṭai vaittup pirinta talaimakaṉ varaivoṭu pukutarā niṉṟāṉ eṉpatu tōḻi kūṟak kēṭṭa talaimakaḷ avaṭkuc colliyatu.  </p>
        <p xml:lang="en">
          What the heroine told the confidante, the heroine who listened as the confidante said that the hero—who had separated, placing a gap in the marriage—is [now] making his approach with marriage.
          
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink253">
<l>kuṉṟak kuṟavaṉ cānta naṟumpukai</l>
<l>tēṅkamaḻ cilampiṉ varaiyakaṅ kamaḻuṅ</l>
<l>kāṉaka nāṭaṉ varaiyiṉ</l>
<l>maṉṟalu muṭaiyaḷko ṟōḻi yāyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>If the man from the forest land,</l>
        <l>where, within the mountain whose slopes are fragrant with honey,</l>
        <l>the fragrant smoke of sandalwood of the hill-dweller is fragrant,</l>
        <l>were to marry [me],</l>
        <l rend="space">would mother accept the marriage too, O friend?</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
